SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:INFO
	"BARTON:\nAmmunition ran out and I've managed to lose my equipment. Great..I need to find Lotos as soon as possible. I wonder if there are zombies around here?"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ARTILLERYDEATH
	"BARTON:\nLong-range guns are disabled. I also reconfigured a certain security system for myself, but I don't see where it is exactly.."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ZOMBEE1
	"BARTON:\nDamn, they're really here - gotta run!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ZARZ1
	"BARTON:\nThe Gates had unlocked. Although it doesn't specify which ones exactly, there's a hint of them being Yellow. Additional information tells that parts of CODE, which will be needed later, is scattered throughout Lab on the Floor. Would be a good idea to write them down whenever I see them."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:REACTOR1
	"BARTON:\nThere is remote access to this reactor. I'll keep it just in case - it might come in handy!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PC1
	"BARTON:\nThere's a PC in front. Need to try to hack it."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:GATTLINGS
	"BARTON:\nI took control of these turrets. However, they are out of power. I can use Reactor overload to power them up - but why would I do that now?"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ZARZ2
	"BARTON:\nAh! Got the Code. So, which pocket did I put my notes in? Anyhow, the Information Board nearby says that if a wrong path is chosen you're punished by an immediate death!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:WEAPON0
	"BARTON:\nIn a Room with a jeep there'll be a PC with which I can unlock Gate leading to Ammunition storage. It also states here that this PC has remote access to a certain Train..."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:WEAPON1
	"BARTON:\nAfter unlocking the next Gate, I will drive this jeep to the Ammo-storage, alongside checking files associated with the Train..."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:WEAPON2
	"BARTON:\nSo, I have 2 UZI's, good shoes and armor - Hold on, Lotos - I'm coming!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:BEFOREBOSS
	"BARTON:\nI think I see some kind of Large silhouette from here, it's scary. Right behind it is a chamber with Lotos inside..."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:VIPIL
	"BARTON:\nSelf-destruct system activated! In a few minutes everything here will go to Hell - we need to get out of here!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:KLYUCHUTRUPA01
	"BARTON:\nFound a fancy KEY, it appears to unlock some kind of system. I'll probably keep it for myself - might come into play later on"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:KLYUCHUTRUPA02
	"BARTON:\nGot another KEY to keep for myself"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PKZ14-0KL
	"BARTON:\nThe control panel is locked. There are documents here, detailing that to unlock it you need 7 keys, which are in the possession of 7 Scientists. I need to find them to move on"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PKZ14-1KL
	"BARTON:\nThe control panel is locked. There are documents here, detailing that to unlock it you need 7 keys, which are in the possession of 7 Scientists. It looks like I already found 1 on the corpse. I need to find the rest"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PKZ14-2KL
	"BARTON:\nThe control panel is locked. There are documents here, detailing that to unlock it you need 7 keys, which are in the possession of 7 Scientists. It looks like I already found 2 on the corpse. I need to find the rest"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:2STULA
	"BARTON:\nRelyng on these soldiers was a mistake, take the KEY and go"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PKZ14-LOHKL
	"BARTON:\nI took KEY from this pathetic piece of crap"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:UCHBOSSMOSHNII
	"BARTON:\nWon't be able to get close to this scientist - guard are set on him. I have an idea - I need to go back to the PC this scientist just worked on before."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ZOMBEEMOI
	"BARTON:\nI temporarily seize control of these towers affecting the zombies. Looks like that guard is in trouble now, hehehe))"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ZOMBEENEUBIY
	"BARTON:\nI don't think I should kill them. These zombies can still serve me"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ROBOTS1
	"BARTON:\nLooks like he's being guarded by these robots. There are others here, it appears they're off. I need to find the RadioTower and take control of them, in which case I can get to this bloody bastard!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:ROBOTS2
	"BARTON:\nRadio Tower is now mine! Now I can remove this annoying obstacle.."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PKZ14-DRONEKL
	"BARTON:\nCombat drones didn't help him - Yet I got the KEY"
END

