END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:GATTLIG2
	"BARTON:\nThat asshole managed to hide behind a Turret. Now I need to turn off its power. Damn it, but I could have tried to kill him before he reached the control panel"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:GATTLIG3
	"BARTON:\nNo matter how long they hide, all the KEYs will be mine. This one is already"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:HAKKERMAN01
	"Hakkerman:\nI'll help you with the Train. Just clear the way for me to the Main Control Panel."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:HAKKERMAN02
	"SupaHakka:\nI'll wait here for now and study this data. Clear the way for me!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:HAKKERMAN03
	"Daru:\nDr.Trax is blocking the system from the other side - distract him and I'll take care of the Train."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:FIRSTVR
	"BARTON:\nBlocked. I need to somehow open this gate - it looks like there is an electronic lock with remote access."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:FIRSTARMORY
	"BARTON:\nOn the gate it is written - Armory. It seems that I can get armor and weapons there."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:FIRSTEXPW
	"BARTON:\nOn the gate it is written - experimental weapon room. Dr.Pipkin has the Key."
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:TOXREACTOR
	"BARTON:\nI need to somehow disable this Reactor. I know only one way - to explode!"
END

