SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PILOT01
	"Hakkerman:\nWe need to split up, otherwise we won't make it in time. You must open that Gate for me"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PILOT02
	"Hakkerman:\nand I will open the Pilot's cell. Then we will unite and get out of here all together!"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PILOT03
	"Hakkerman:\nI'm there, waiting for you to open the Gate for me"
END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:PILOT04
