END

SCRIPT:MSNSTR:RB:DE:HAKERPOMERDAIHUYSNIM
	"Barton:\nAh, Hakkerman is dead! If I could rewind time, but I can't...Well, the exit is open, I still have to try to get out of here- goodbye Pilot, I won't forget you."
END
